features: LONG LASTING POWER: This pack of 4 AA Type batteries with low self discharge is ideal for devices with high power consumption including TV & AV remotes, wireless keyboard & mouse, doorbells and clocks - These batteries guarantee long-lasting power
HIGH SAFETY STANDARDS: These rechargeable batteries comply with current valid EU directive and meet the highest requirements for safety and longevity with good cycle stability

PACK OF 4: This pack consists of 4 x AA Size NiMH MaxE Pro 2500mAh ANSMANN rechargeable batteries. These batteries have been successfully tested for electrical, thermal, geometric and mechanical requirements

RECHARGEABLE: These rechargeable batteries can be charged with high charging current resulting in shorter charging time. These batteries also guarantee longer running time all thanks to the high capacity

SAVE MONEY: These NiMH batteries can be recharged up to 1000 times saving you money and reducing waste! These batteries are an economical replacement for disposable / alkaline batteries - These batteries retain 80% charge for up to one year in storage

OTHER USES: Use with trackball, Apple mouse keyboard & trackpad, garage door remote controller, flashlight, kids toy, electronic pets, radio controlled car kids, alarm burglar sensors & system, alarm clock, remote control, flash gun, flashgun, Glade auto spray air freshener, Airwick air freshener, diffuser, thermometer, torch, mini sewing machine, travel electric razor, shaver, eyebrow nose & facial trimmer, handheld fan
description: From the manufacturer Rechargeable battery with low self-discharge for devices with high power consumption Optimal solution for demanding users: The batteries have a high capacity, and still a very low self-discharge. It is thus ideal for applications such as flashlights, toys, modelling, game consoles, digital cameras, flash equipment, medical equipment etc. maxE has the energy to power all your devices. The self-discharge is 10 times lower than in regular NiMH batteries. After a year, there is still around 80% of the initial capacity left. This was made possible by a special separator which dramatically reduces unwanted internal current flow. Benefits the environment and your wallet NiMH batteries can generally be used wherever disposable batteries are used. This allows you to save money and protect the environment. A rechargeable battery can replace many hundreds to thousands of batteries! Fast charging + no memory effect The batteries can be charged with a high charging current, thereby very short charging times are possible. With the latest battery technology, the memory effect is ruled out even after several partial charges. What is maxE? The self-discharge is 10 times lower than in normal NiMH batteries. After one year they still retain up 95% of the initial capacity. This is made possible by a special insultator which dramatically reduces the unwanted internal current flow. As the batteries are supplied pre-charged, they can be used immediately. Economical and benefits the environment Sustainable from beginning to end Ideal for power intensive applications ANSMANN Portable Power Solutions Primary and Rechargeable Batteries Coin Cells and Camera Batteries Power banks and Battery Chargers Torches, Headlights and LED Floodlights Travel Adaptors and Power Supplies
